asset.title: Element Presents The Northern Wheels Tour
asset.description:
To celebrate the launch of the second capsule collection with Element Advocate and illustrator Chad Eaton aka TIMBER!, Element presents "The Northern Wheels Tour": A bike tour from Paris to Belgium - following the collection's inspiration and Element's motto “Keep discovering” - while traveling across countries on a bike. 

The passionate cyclist Chad Eaton took the challenge and rode the tour from Paris to Belgium through the famous bicycle road race “Paris – Roubaix" on his specially manufactured bike by legendary Alex Singer Bicycle Shop Paris.
